thou shalt fall upon the open fields; thou shalt not be brought together, nor gathered: I have given thee for meat to the beasts of the field and to the fowls of the heaven.","year":-589},{"id":"recQm137i7sF2TMmk","ref":"Ezek.29.6","text":"And all the inhabitants of Egypt shall know that I am the LORD, because they have been a staff of reed to the house of Israel.","year":-589},{"id":"recplDi5vgqGSSead","ref":"Ezek.29.7","text":"When they took hold of thee by thy hand, thou didst break, and rend all their shoulder: and when they leaned upon thee, thou brakest, and madest all their loins to be at a stand.","year":-589},{"id":"recGzmyjVHaIC3jxQ","ref":"Ezek.29.8","text":"Therefore thus saith the Lord GOD; Behold, I will bring a sword upon thee, and cut off man and beast out of thee.","year":-589}]}
